00:31:06.372 --> 00:31:07.788
of people who get
in touch with us

00:31:07.788 --> 00:31:09.540
and really want to
share in this movement.

00:31:09.540 --> 00:31:11.750
So I'm definitely willing
to listen and work

00:31:11.750 --> 00:31:13.649
with you on that, too.

